  m_Name: Aegis Before Oldrion
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: Aegis Before Oldrion
    lines:
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "My knight. I see you\u2019ve found Isovios. Immortality, it promises,
        and I am all that stands in your way. I know this story all too well. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Boss Oldrion
      expression: 
      line: 'Caspian? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'I could never have foreseen it. Not even as you plunged the blade into
        me.  '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'You were always at my side, even long before it became your duty. We
        may not have always seen eye to eye, but you were steadfast. Loyal. To die
        by your hand seemed so impossible it never even crossed my mind. And yet.. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Boss Oldrion
      expression: 
      line: 'Speak, spectre! What is the meaning of this? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "You can still turn back. It doesn\u2019t have to end like this, Orion.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: "I know you\u2019re scared. It scares all of us. Even kings succumb to
        it eventually. But today needn\u2019t be that day. Not for me. Not for you.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'This kingdom is your home. You belong here, with me.  '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'Destroying your only bond and your home in one fell swoop will do nothing
        but displace you! You will never again feel the comfort and joy of community,
        of companionship. Is that what you want? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Boss Oldrion
      expression: 
      line: 'It is all meaningless! Temporary! Everything I care about will always
        slip through my fingers no matter how hard I clutch onto it. My parents...
        Even my own life. Time crunches us all beneath its feet like some uncaring
        machine! Isovios is the only thing that will free me of this curse! '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: King Aegis
      expression: 
      line: 'Please, Orion. I know you. This is not what you truly want. I promise
        you. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Boss Oldrion
      expression: 
      line: I will not be dissuaded by some ghast! I have made my choice. Move aside!
      audio: {fileID: 0}
